schemaVersion: 1
id: youtube-channel-factory-root
name: YouTube Channel Factory
kind: root
version: 0.1.0
description: >
  A complete YouTube OS in a directory. Fill in three placeholders (who you are,
  what your channel is about, your style and format), run the bootstrap prompt,
  and a creative-director agent builds out your channel brand, a 12-video
  content calendar, scripts, thumbnail prompts, and a production-gear decision
  guide (DSLR vs mirrorless vs phone, editing software, audio chain).
entry: index.md
